content_copy
expand_less
pip install pandas scikit-learn statsmodels pyarrow

Run the pipeline:

Execute python src/cleaning.py to process raw data.

Execute python src/modeling.py to generate forecasts and the Tableau export.

Open Tableau: Connect to the file in the output/ folder to view the dashboards.

